pages.pageText: For years have I tended the fires of Lunnum's Pyre. But now the curse of time has taken its toll upon my body. The fires for which I have cared for so long have now begun to dim. I ask for your help in keeping the light of Lunnum's Pyre forever burning. Seek me out on the Isle of Ruin at 89.1N 47.6W.

stringStats.value: Fiun Gaya asks for help in tending the fires of Lunnum's Pyre. This is a good quest for players around level 100.
